Package io.reinert.requestor.core.serialization

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Deserializer<T>
    Performs deserialization of Types.
    HandlesSubTypes<T>
    It tells the SerializerManager to register an abstraction to handle one or more subtypes
    Serializer<T>
    Performs serialization and deserialization of a type to/from plain text.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DeserializationContext
    Context of deserialization.
    SerializationContext
    Context of serialization.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    SerializationException
    SerializationException is the superclass exception related to Serialization issues.
    UnableToDeserializeException
    Represents an error occurred during deserialization.
    UnableToSerializeException
    Represents an error occurred during serialization.
